#### text ####
text: The next day we had an afternoon shinkansen so we spent the morning at museums in northern Tokyo. We had an hour before our next museum opened so we visited the nearby Bonsai Museum first. I didn't know what to expect, but it ended up being one of our favourites of the trip! The museum started with a guide to understanding and appreciating bonsai before turning us loose in a courtyard full of beautiful examples.
