#### text ####
text: After seeing all those trains in the museum it was time to get on our own shinkansen and go aaaaaall the way north to Hakodate, on Japan's northern island. It was on the shinkansen, so it was a nice smooth ride. It never fails to surprise me how quickly the scenery goes from farms to dense housing and back again.
